  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "You'll notice some function have a brackets i.e `()` while others don't.\n",
    "- **Attribute**: Without parenthesis, they store information/ some meta information about the data/dataframe\n",
    "- **Function**: With parenthesis,  they perform some operations/steps"
